rows.label: qst100408_msg0001
rows.name:
The flyers were a huge success, mo!
Thanks to you, more customers are coming
for the singing and the food, mo!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0002
rows.name:
And because I cooked so much,
I've gotten way better at
making it delicious, mo!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm sure the rumors of Falala
will reach my son Solala...

rows.label: qst100408_msg0004
rows.name:
But just reaching him
isn't enough, mo...

rows.label: qst100408_msg0005
rows.name:
I want him to come back,
mo... I want to see him
healthy and happy, mo...

rows.label: qst100408_msg0006
rows.name:
Thank you, mo... Have you
heard any rumors about Solala
during your travels, mo?

rows.label: qst100408_msg0007
rows.name:
Is that so, mo... I want to hear
rumors from more people, mo!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0008
rows.name:
Falala will also go to the
informant's office, mo!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0101
rows.name:
I need to save money to buy
information from the informant, mo.

rows.label: qst100408_msg0102
rows.name:
I wish I could hear information about
Solala from more people, mo...
